WEBVTT

00:02:56.518 --> 00:03:00.894
to behold the legendary
"warm stream of the Amazon."

00:03:02.671 --> 00:03:04.292
But then ...

00:03:04.316 --> 00:03:05.638
I heard something,

00:03:07.255 --> 00:03:08.704
a low surge

00:03:10.347 --> 00:03:13.042
that got louder and louder

00:03:13.792 --> 00:03:15.260
as we came closer.

00:03:16.300 --> 00:03:20.228
It sounded like ocean waves
constantly crashing,

00:03:20.252 --> 00:03:24.937
and as we got closer, I saw smoke, vapor,
coming up through the trees.

00:03:24.961 --> 00:03:28.260
And then, I saw this.

00:03:29.791 --> 00:03:32.260
I immediately grabbed for my thermometer,